{"tid":1080102,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人拎講談社漫畫比賽大賞！","createTime":"2019-03-27T11:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T23:51:36.000Z","uid":191473,"like":105,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"76ffded7c23646f47833005ad41e2a22c2194c4e","tid":1080102,"uid":191473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:11:43.000Z","msg":"朋友贏左「講談社」輕小說編輯部漫畫比賽嘅特別大賞！<br />\n講談社就係果間《週刊少年Magazine》《月到少年magazine》嘅公司（間公司出名作品有《妖精的尾巴》《七大罪》《飛輪少年》等等）<br />\n人地原本規則係得獎者有10萬日圓同責任編輯跟進<br />\n佢竟然得到特別賞20萬日圓同責任編輯跟進！<br />\n<br />\n官網有圖有真相<br />\n好似會喺日本果本月刊實體書再公佈多次<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LWczmr4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLWczmr4.png&h=8f1c66a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MRnLs6r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMRnLs6r.png&h=04a79c46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次真係拋頭露面喇！<br />\n<br />\n比埋作者個page大家望下<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/K9ehvvf%E7%9A%84%E5%89%B5%E4%BD%9C%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93-550778138751291/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FK9ehvvf%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2589%25B5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E9%2596%2593-550778138751291%2F&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTlxfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=91eb196b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/K9ehvvf%E7%9A%84%E5%89%B5%E4%BD%9C%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93-550778138751291/</a><br />\n<br />\n不過佢個page而家冇咩野睇....."},{"pid":"d4dacd94d474c2a0f6387cabfa5ec26e2472ff5c","tid":1080102,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":25,"score":-25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:22:58.000Z","msg":"拋頭露面？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb620a68418f3fdb7bb012a9d7b80d51e7d5fe1","tid":1080102,"uid":191473,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"d4dacd94d474c2a0f6387cabfa5ec26e2472ff5c","tid":1080102,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike